# MCP Example 5 - Semantic Query (Zapper)

This example demonstrates semantic-query runtime end-to-end over the Zapper domain.

<Highlight type="info" title="What this verifies">
Retrieval -> Join path -> AST generation -> AST validation -> SQL compile -> SQL execute -> summary -> planner final answer.
</Highlight>

